data.description: IMMEDIATELY AVAILABLE: Don't miss this 2021 built gem, a stunning single-family home nestled in the heart of Taneytown. This traditional residence has 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, this home provides ample space for both relaxation and entertaining.  Interior featuring granite countertops and  stainless steel appliances in the kitchen. The sleek and stylish kitchen is not only a chef's dream but also a focal point for gatherings with family and friends.  The open floor plan seamlessly connects the kitchen to the living and dining areas, creating a spacious and inviting atmosphere. Large windows throughout the home flood the space with natural light, enhancing the bright and airy ambiance.  The master suite is a true retreat, offering a peaceful haven with a private en-suite bath. Three additional bedrooms provide versatility for guest rooms, a home office, or whatever suits your lifestyle. The 2.5 baths feature modern fixtures and finishes, adding a touch of luxury to your daily routine.  For convenience, this home comes complete with a double car garage and driveway for 4 additional vehicles, ensuring that parking is never a concern. The exterior of the property is surrounded by a well-maintained yard in a quiet community, providing a tranquil setting for relaxation.  Situated in a serene neighborhood,  offers the perfect blend of suburban tranquility and modern convenience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this stylish and contemporary residence your own. Contact us today to schedule a showing and experience the charm of Taneytown living at its finest.
